title: O'Neill CWC New Zealand 11 - Finals re-edit
description: Adam Melling is the first O'Neill Coldwater Classic New Zealand Champion. William Cardoso second. Happy Birthday to Adam. A big thank you to everybody in Gisborne and see you up North in Scotland!
